{"tid":2382142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳3冗員引發內亂搞走林伯","createTime":"2021-01-27T05:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T23:32:14.000Z","uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4fcf3ad208baafa925339a65ac354e891bad4a","tid":2382142,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"林柏特在周一被車路士摘去烏紗，據知其中一個原因是有部份不受重用的球員，令更衣室爆發內亂。  <br />\n<br />\n根據英國《每日電訊報》報道，林柏特（Frank Lampard）在今季豪擲2.3億鎊擴軍，而且重用青訓小將，可是未能縮減人手，一眾冗員便因為不滿，造成更衣室內亂。 <strong><span class=\"red\">中堅魯迪加（Antonio Rudiger）、左閘馬高斯阿朗素、中場佐真奴是始作俑者</span></strong>，當中已經淪為中堅第5選擇的魯迪加，多次在操練時與隊長艾斯比列古達發生衝突。 另外，林伯明顯偏心於青訓小將，中場曼治便曾被嘲諷為「老師的寵物」，令不少球員都心生不滿。艾斯比列古達努力消除球員間的心結，始終未能成功。 事實上，林柏特也看到問題所在，在對上2場英超都派出魯迪加踢正選，只是為時已晚，自己先下台。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">又捉鬼</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thechelseachronicle.com/static/uploads/17/2020/07/GettyImages-1256183905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechelseachronicle.com%2Fstatic%2Fuploads%2F17%2F2020%2F07%2FGettyImages-1256183905.jpg&h=a6399200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/Chelsea-transfer-news-Lampard-Jorginho-Gilmour-1304167.jpg?r=1593695012680\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2FChelsea-transfer-news-Lampard-Jorginho-Gilmour-1304167.jpg%3Fr%3D1593695012680&h=b38daeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d3vlf99qeg6bpx.cloudfront.net/content/uploads/2019/10/19172331/chelsea.newcastle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd3vlf99qeg6bpx.cloudfront.net%2Fcontent%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F19172331%2Fchelsea.newcastle.jpg&h=6d09b83a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5